metadata.name: ROODHRA
metadata.description:
Lord Shiva/Roodhra is regarded as the representation of the Supreme Being.Shiva,in his most violent and furious form to be specific. He is one of the three celestial beings believed to have created the universe. One who drives away evil; one who is praiseworthy.It also means 'roarer' or 'howler', when associated with the God of storms.

Every element shown here depicts something in the spiritual science.

THE CRESENT MOON, THE BLUSIH HUE, THE SNAKE, THE TRIDENT, THE DAMRU AND THE THIRD EYE
